<template><div><p>系统的频率特性描述了系统对正弦输入的稳态响应，当输入为<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\sin(\omega t)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mop">sin</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>，经过系统后输出为<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi>ω</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>ϕ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A(\omega)\sin[\omega t + \phi(\omega)]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mop">sin</span><span class="mopen">[</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">ϕ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mclose">)]</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<p>我们设设系统的传递函数为<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">G(s)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">s</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>系统输出信号的稳态响应相对其正弦输入信号的幅值之比<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>j</mi><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A(\omega) = |G(j\omega)|</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">jω</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mord">∣</span></span></span></span>为系统的幅频特性，描述系统在稳态下响应不同频率的正弦输入时在幅值上的增益特性。</p>
<p>系统输出信号的稳态响应相对其正弦输入信号的相移<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>ϕ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∠</mi><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>j</mi><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\phi(\omega) = \angle G(j\omega)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">ϕ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">∠</span><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">jω</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>为系统的相频特性，描述系统在稳态下响应不同频率的正弦输入时在相位上产生的滞后<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>ϕ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\phi(s) &lt; 0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">ϕ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">s</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">&lt;</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>或超前<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>ϕ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\phi(s) &gt; 0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">ϕ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">s</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">&gt;</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<h4 id="系统的频率特性的表现形式" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#系统的频率特性的表现形式" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 系统的频率特性的表现形式</h4>
<figure><img src="@source/subjects/CE/_images/F434d569Df202312111134568.png" alt="" tabindex="0" loading="lazy"><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<p>系统的频率特性是一种复变函数，设<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>U</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">U(\omega)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>为实部，称为实频特性，<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>V</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">V(\omega)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">V</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>为虚部，称为虚频特性。</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mtable rowspacing="0.25em" columnalign="right left" columnspacing="0em"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>j</mi><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>U</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>j</mi><mi>V</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>ϕ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>j</mi><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>ϕ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mi>j</mi><mi>ϕ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></msup></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>j</mi><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∠</mi><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>j</mi><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\begin{aligned}
G(j\omega) &amp;= U(\omega) + jV(\omega) \\
&amp;= A(\omega)[\cos \phi(\omega) + j \sin \phi(\omega)] \\
&amp;= A(\omega)e^{j\phi(\omega)} \\
&amp;= |G(j\omega)| \angle G(j\omega)
\end{aligned}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:6.098em;vertical-align:-2.799em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mtable"><span class="col-align-r"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:3.299em;"><span style="top:-5.459em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">jω</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.959em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"></span></span><span style="top:-2.361em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"></span></span><span style="top:-0.861em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:2.799em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="col-align-l"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:3.299em;"><span style="top:-5.459em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">jV</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.959em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mopen">[</span><span class="mop">cos</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">ϕ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05724em;">j</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mop">sin</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">ϕ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mclose">)]</span></span></span><span style="top:-2.361em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">e</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.938em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.05724em;">j</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">ϕ</span><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="top:-0.861em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">jω</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mord">∣∠</span><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">jω</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:2.799em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>j</mi><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi>U</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi>V</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
